This paper discusses the implementation of MyCaffe, a deep learning system, and its architecture. The paper also talks about the newly added MyCaffeTrainerRL for Reinforcement Learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
